18:35.245 --> 18:37.717
IT'S ALWAYS FUN TO SEE
THE TALENT UP CLOSE

18:37.717 --> 18:39.749
BEFORE YOU MAKE YOUR PICKS.
HEY, MOM.

18:39.749 --> 18:42.392
OH, TRAVIS COBB.
LET'S SEE. YES.

18:42.392 --> 18:44.354
TRAVIS GETS SCOOPED UP
IN THE EARLY ROUNDS.

18:44.354 --> 18:45.695
(whispers) CONGRATS.

18:45.695 --> 18:48.127
PLEASE GO SIT
VERY FAR AWAY.

18:48.127 --> 18:50.400
в™Є HAPPY в™Є

18:50.400 --> 18:51.731
I FEEL VIOLATED.

18:51.731 --> 18:53.763
LOOK AT YOU IN YOUR OUTFIT.

18:53.763 --> 18:55.335
I KNOW. I'M ADORABLE.
(chuckles)

18:55.335 --> 18:58.338
OH. BY THE WAY, MY SPEECH
IS MOSTLY ABOUT DAD,

18:58.338 --> 19:01.341
JUST BECAUSE, YOU KNOW,
HE'S ALWAYS SO HARD ON HIMSELF,

19:01.341 --> 19:03.843
SAYING HOW HE PEAKED
IN HIGH SCHOOL, AND I JUST

19:03.843 --> 19:06.346
WANTED TO DO SOMETHING NICE
FOR HIM, YOU KNOW?

19:06.346 --> 19:08.418
I THINK THAT'S GREAT.

19:08.418 --> 19:10.420
THAT'S WHY YOU'RE SO AMAZING,

19:10.420 --> 19:12.922
BECAUSE YOU JUST
DO ALL THIS STUFF FOR ME,

19:12.922 --> 19:15.425
AND YOU NEVER ASK
FOR ANYTHING IN RETURN,

19:15.425 --> 19:18.188
AND I HOPE YOU KNOW
HOW GRATEFUL I AM.

19:18.188 --> 19:20.260
MM-HMM. (sniffles)

19:20.260 --> 19:22.161
THAT'S MY NOISE. (chuckles)

19:22.161 --> 19:23.493
LOVE YOU, MOM.

19:23.493 --> 19:25.195
I LOVE YOU.

19:25.195 --> 19:26.736
в™Є WHAT YOU'RE LOOKING FOR в™Є

19:26.736 --> 19:29.899
MM, OKAY.
YOU KNOCK 'EM DEAD.

19:29.899 --> 19:31.901
в™Є NOTHIN' MORE в™Є

19:31.901 --> 19:35.305
в™Є LOST SOMEWHERE OVER
