19:42.412 --> 19:44.484
в™Є HAPPY в™Є
RIDICULOUS.

19:44.484 --> 19:46.786
в™Є HAPPY в™Є

19:46.786 --> 19:49.359
в™Є HAPPINESS в™Є

19:49.359 --> 19:52.662
в™Є LOST SOMEWHERE OVER
THE RAINBOW'S END в™Є

19:52.662 --> 19:55.365
OKAY, I'M GONNA TAKE TURNS
CRYING ON EACH OF YOU,

19:55.365 --> 19:56.666
ALL RIGHT?

19:56.666 --> 19:58.368
GO CRAZY.
SOUNDS GOOD.

19:58.368 --> 19:59.699
TRAV'S ABOUT TO SPEAK.

20:00.870 --> 20:02.502
в™Є PURSUIT OF HAPPINESS в™Є

20:02.502 --> 20:03.873
DUDE, LOOK!

20:05.335 --> 20:07.477
