I CAN FEEL IT IN MY BONES.

20:07.477 --> 20:08.978
(lowered voice) HEY! NO!

20:08.978 --> 20:11.611
FOR ONCE, WE ARE NOT
GOING TO EMBARRASS HIM.

20:11.611 --> 20:12.882
NO!

20:12.882 --> 20:14.484
(amplified voice) HOWDY, FOLKS.

20:14.484 --> 20:16.486
в™Є SMILE, EVERYBODY, HAPPINESS в™Є

20:16.486 --> 20:20.290
NO, NOPE. UH...

20:20.290 --> 20:22.292
MY NAME IS TRAVIS COBB...

20:22.292 --> 20:26.426
в™Є IS EVERYBODY HAPPY?
SMILE, EVERYBODY, HAPPINESS в™Є

20:27.857 --> 20:29.329
(mouths word)

20:31.431 --> 20:34.364
IN THE FOREST OF LIFE--
I LOVE MY DAD! LET'S GET IT!

20:35.635 --> 20:36.636
WHAT?!
AAH!

20:36.636 --> 20:38.638
GO, GO, GO, GO, GO, GO!

20:38.638 --> 20:41.010
(Laurie screams)
DID YOU HEAR THAT?
BEST SPEECH EVER!

20:41.010 --> 20:42.512
в™Є WHAT'S DONE IS DONE в™Є

20:42.512 --> 20:45.014
(screaming)

20:45.014 --> 20:48.448
в™Є STARTIN' OVER AGAIN,
MORE OR LESS в™Є

20:48.448 --> 20:50.450
I'M SORRY.
IT'S REALLY HOT OUT HERE.

20:50.450 --> 20:53.383
YOU CAN GET UNDER, TOO.
ALL RIGHT.

20:53.383 --> 20:55.254
LOOK AT THOSE IDIOTS.

20:55.254 --> 20:57.256
(chuckles)
THEY LOOK ABSURD.

20:57.256 --> 20:59.689
(Bobby and Jules screaming)

20:59.689 --> 21:03.363
в™Є OF HAPPINESS в™Є

21:09.369 --> 21:10.840
WHY'D YOU CALL ME?

21:10.840 --> 21:11.871
LOOK.

21:11.871 --> 21:13.673
EW!

21:13.673 --> 21:15.705
SO... THEY'RE....
UH-HUH.

21:15.705 --> 21:18.708
I DON'T WANT TO SEE THAT.
WHY WOULD YOU MAKE ME SEE THAT?

21:18.708 --> 21:21.581
BECAUSE WE'RE HUNGRY,
